data.description:
Live the Country Trails Life! This Jay Manning quality home is a wonderful location in Country Trails of Harker Heights. Our favorite aesthetic is the Open Floor plan and Upscale Wood Laminate and Tile floors. We enjoy the large space with sitting area and tray ceiling in the Main Bedroom and huge main bathroom with Large Jacuzzi and spacious custom walk in closet. Three Bedrooms and full Bathroom on other side of house  (Right Wing) from Main Suite, providing privacy. Great place for morning coffee on custom designed Porcelain tiled back porch. I also love that the home backs up to Carl Levin Park. Go for a swim in the pool, play a game of ball, enjoy a picnic, take a stroll on the paved path as the Ducks play in the park pond. Its like you are downtown, but have the beauty of the country right out your back yard.There is even a Community Garden at the Park.  Near City Hall, Restaurants, Retail Stores. Shopping Mall just across the Highway. Need quick access to the freeway to go to Austin, Waco, or Dallas, this is the place for you. Never fear if Local Electric goes out, with wood or gas burning fireplace right in the Family Room.
Rare Homes for sale on Grizzly in established Country Trails...
Owner is Licensed Real Estate Broker in state of Hawaii. Will work with Agents.
